item.title: Fall 2020 Interest Meeting
item.description: The Fall 2020 interest meeting will be held in the week of Nov 23rd, 2020. Please fill out this membership interest form (https://forms.gle/X2k8scLqNkgsvLv1A) to specify your availability and express your interest to join the Yale Undergrad Quantum Computing group. Slides and more information will be added after the interest meeting!
